nodes.text: So does this mean they have to get tougher on gun control or softer before the results go their way? That is the real question. My guess is that we are caught in the unhappy medium where going in either direction will be more successful than where we are now.
So then will you go the way on liberty (repeal stoopid laws) or tyranny (enact more unconstitutional laws)?
Your link has nothing about Isreal or the Swiss in it.
